{"tid":1641433,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"撐Pokémon GO火箭隊都要道歉？內地網民質疑「中體體育」反應過敏","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T08:09:49.000Z","uid":130626,"like":205,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"2ebb583765fddd752ad30be5b58dc411eb2359c7","tid":1641433,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:33:27.000Z","msg":"香港反送中的蝴蝶效應，因NBA火箭隊總經理莫利日前的撐港言論，已發酵至中國全面封殺NBA中國賽，「火箭隊」也在微博上被大批網民圍攻。不過有中國網民在facebook上用Pok&eacute;mon GO中的知名反派組織「火箭隊」來揶揄此事，卻被任職公司要求道歉，就連中國網民也大表質疑：「這樣要道歉？」<br />\n中國馬拉松賽事營運公司「中體體育」員工邱冠榮，日前在FB貼文以Pok&eacute;mon GO「火箭隊」來揶揄近來NBA火箭隊遭中國抵制一事，內容寫到「我還是會支持火箭隊的，無論你們怎麼詆毀他們，畢竟是我從小的信仰，他們一次次慘痛失敗但又一次次爬起來像夢想挑戰，激勵我無數個奮鬥的日日夜夜。謝謝你，武藏、小次郎、喵喵怪。」<br />\n不料邱冠榮發表此貼文後被公司「中體體育」要求他寫道歉信，並於今日在微博「中體馬拉松」貼出道歉信內容。「中體體育」在微博表示：「我司員工邱冠榮在朋友圈發表不當言論，造成不良的社會影響。事件發生後，我司已對其進行嚴肅批評教育，邱冠榮已認到言論的不當之處，並作出深刻反省檢討。」<br />\n「中體體育」的道歉聲明一出，馬上引起網民熱議，不過大多數認為該公司無限上綱且反應過度，紛紛留言：「這需要道歉？」「諧音梗有人聽不懂？」「靠這蹭熱度啊？」「拿這個梗開玩笑的朋友不少啊，難道都要道歉？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191009/large/1570608971_7119.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191009%2Flarge%2F1570608971_7119.jpg&h=ee9b69cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191009/60134235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191009%2F60134235&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=836115a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191009%2F60134235&h=3d62343d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191009/60134235</a>"},{"pid":"6cc1a0c36b057ccc0f83c12f99fc12932fa1b1d5","tid":1641433,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:35:52.000Z","msg":"國際文宣組全面進化，大型國際文宣活動&quot;What if they own it&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5237a7505be4b6efa58608b0e335e88ad0acdcbb","tid":1641433,"uid":59175,"like":111,"dislike":2,"score":109,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2015/52/02/qZqVpqSXlqacrKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2015%2F52%2F02%2FqZqVpqSXlqacrKU.jpg&h=f779cef8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01151cfddc707dff921d936ea864b605db0a73fe","tid":1641433,"uid":65449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47aacb295ed80fb1ae6c9cc7816665d1298bde89","tid":1641433,"uid":259675,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:39:55.000Z","msg":"再見了喵喵怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdc5088d7140c3156bdc27724967915fdd22342","tid":1641433,"uid":19660,"like":102,"dislike":0,"score":102,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"井底蛙以為自己真係有自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d13b0f49e287a09f8fd2333b1a6e5a070820f3","tid":1641433,"uid":301989,"like":69,"dislike":2,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:40:53.000Z","msg":"收皮啦支那人 你哋遲啲呼吸都係罪 比人捉撚咗入集中營唔好問點解 係你班撚樣自己攞嚟 抵撚死"},{"pid":"0a212c7d86f4bdc92a8212c550d8e100ea5c14a4","tid":1641433,"uid":235015,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:41:28.000Z","msg":"岩呀，全部都反中辱華，全部都要道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dc2feb8480f0aae0a249912a8e30a75d1eb82f","tid":1641433,"uid":55511,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"